			<li id="copyrightBlock">
				<h1>
					<a name="copyright">
						Intellectual property
					</a>
				</h1>
				<h2>My stance</h2>
				<p>
					Respecting intellectual property is important.
					Copyright infringement is not stealing, but it is
						wrong.
